descriptionNullable:
These files contains information on Japanese voice actors (mainly for anime and games).
The database is being organized by Hitoshi Doi, and contains contributions by lots of people.
I just cleaned a little bit the most important ones and included the columns that I think will be the most useful.

Hitoshi Doi [Seiyuu database](http://www.usagi.org/doi/seiyuu/)
raw files [link](http://www.usagi.org/doi/seiyuu/databases.html)
